Nordcurrent also reserves the right to remove User Content from the Pocket Styler Studio for inactive Creators.
Inactivity
shall be defined as a Creator’s failure to sign in to the Pocket Styler Studio for a continuous period of one year (i.e., 365 days). In such cases, Nordcurrent shall issue a notice to the Creator’s email or other agreed-upon communications 335 days after the last sign-in, informing them of the impending removal of their User Content in 30 days if the Creator does not return to activity. For clarity, under this clause, Nordcurrent shall only remove User Content projects from the Pocket Styler Studio that have not yet been exported to the Pocket Styler Game.
