Selling on the Services.
Creator acknowledges that Nordcurrent may, through the Services, display, host, and sell the User Content created by Creator to be enjoyed by other Users through the Services. Nordcurrent may make available Creators User Content for sale to other Users in the Services. The Virtual Currency received from the sale of the User Content belongs to Nordcurrent, however, Nordcurrent may allocate some of these funds to the Creator at its discretion.
